data.title: Mishti’s Fashion Blogging Journey
data.meta_description: Mishti Rahman is a Australian Bangladeshi has built her career as an international model, blogger and influencer with a distinctive style.
data.text:
Mishti Rahman is a Bangladeshi-Australian Muslim woman who was born on 10 November 1992 in Adelaide, Australia. Both her mother and father were from Bangladesh. She completed her tutoring at an obscure tuition-based school in Sydney. Her identity is of Bengali-Muslim and she currently lives in Sydney with her family.

Mishti Rahman is a 30 year old model, blogger, and influencer. She’s passionate about helping women in their 20s and 30s find confidence in their own skin. Her blog posts discuss body positivity, self-esteem, beauty, fashion and more.

Mishti had a passion for fashion even at a young age. That’s when she decided to share her passion with the world and started posting fashion and makeup videos on her Instagram account. With over 545k of followers on her Instagram account, she has succeeded in creating the perfect platform to post her fashion blogs and influencer videos. She posts videos, pictures and animations of herself in the latest fashions.

Mishti Rahman has also become a successful beauty entrepreneur and the founder of Mishti Makeup. Mishti’s makeup line has been successful in India and has attracted the attention of international beauty brands. She has endorsed plenty of international brands on her account such as Louis Vuitton, Adore Beauty and many more.
